rComments: Was taught by this prof some years ago.  I have very fond memories of him and his class.  Good teacher and nice man.
Taught classes with enthusiasm.  Quite cute in a geeky English prof kind of way.  Very approachable and friendly.  Helpful and knowledgeable.

extremely well prepared for courses.Lectures filled with interesting anecdotes and information about the texts and authors. Easily accessible, flexible with extensions. He took each student as a whole into consideration. Good comments on essays and tests
